dct_title_s: Washington and vicinity, Maryland, Virginia, District of Columbia
dct_description_sm: Alternate title in right lower margin: Washington and vicinity, Md.-Va.-D.C. Polyconic projection. Relief shown by 10 feet contour intervals. Topography by plane-table methods 1913015 and 1941-42. Revised 1949 from aerial photographs and by plane-table methods. Aerial photographs taken 1949. U.S.G.S. United States. Geological Survey
